"""Test get_ports_from_port_group."""
port_group_name, port_group_details = self.create_port_group()
port_list = self.provisioning.get_ports_from_port_group(port_group_name)
self.assertIsNotNone(port_list)
self.assertIsInstance(port_list, list)
reference_port = port_group_details[constants.SYMMETRIX_PORT_KEY][0][
    constants.PORT_ID]
result_port = port_list[0]
self.assertEqual(reference_port, result_port)
self.assertIsNotNone(re.match(constants.PORT_SEARCH_PATTERN, result_port))
